{"ja446:0.1":"Jataka ","ja446:0.2":"Dasakanipata ","ja446:0.3":"Catudvaravagga ","ja446:0.4":"8. Takkalajataka ","ja446:1.1":"“Na takkala santi na aluvani, ","ja446:1.2":"Na bilaliyo na kalambani tata; ","ja446:1.3":"Eko arannamhi susanamajjhe, ","ja446:1.4":"Kimatthiko tata khanasi kasum”. ","ja446:2.1":"“Pitamaho tata sudubbalo te, ","ja446:2.2":"Anekabyadhihi dukhena phuttho; ","ja446:2.3":"Tamajjaham nikhanissami sobbhe, ","ja446:2.4":"Na hissa tam jivitam rocayami”. ","ja446:3.1":"“Sankappametam patiladdha papakam, ","ja446:3.2":"Accahitam kamma karosi luddam; ","ja446:3.3":"Mayapi tata patilacchase tuvam, ","ja446:3.4":"Etadisam kamma jarupanito; ","ja446:3.5":"Tam kullavattam anuvattamano, ","ja446:3.6":"Ahampi tam nikhanissami sobbhe”. ","ja446:4.1":"“Pharusahi vacahi pakubbamano, ","ja446:4.2":"Asajja mam tvam vadase kumara; ","ja446:4.3":"Putto mamam orasako samano, ","ja446:4.4":"Ahitanukampi mama tvamsi putta”. ","ja446:5.1":"“Na taham tata ahitanukampi, ","ja446:5.2":"Hitanukampi te ahampi tata; ","ja446:5.3":"Papanca tam kamma pakubbamanam, ","ja446:5.4":"Arahami no varayitum tato”. ","ja446:6.1":"“Yo mataram va pitaram savittha, ","ja446:6.2":"Adusake himsati papadhammo; ","ja446:6.3":"Kayassa bheda abhisamparayam, ","ja446:6.4":"Asamsayam so nirayam upeti. ","ja446:7.1":"Yo mataram va pitaram savittha, ","ja446:7.2":"Annena panena upatthahati; ","ja446:7.3":"Kayassa bheda abhisamparayam, ","ja446:7.4":"Asamsayam so sugatim upeti. ","ja446:8.1":"Na me tvam putta ahitanukampi, ","ja446:8.2":"Hitanukampi me tvamsi putta; ","ja446:8.3":"Ahanca tam matara vuccamano, ","ja446:8.4":"Etadisam kamma karomi luddam”. ","ja446:9.1":"“Ya te sa bhariya anariyarupa, ","ja446:9.2":"Mata mamesa sakiya janetti; ","ja446:9.3":"Niddhapaye tanca saka agara, ","ja446:9.4":"Annampi te sa dukhamavaheyya. ","ja446:10.1":"Ya te sa bhariya anariyarupa, ","ja446:10.2":"Mata mamesa sakiya janetti; ","ja446:10.3":"Danta karenuva vasupanita, ","ja446:10.4":"Sa papadhamma punaravajatu”ti. ","ja446:11.1":"Takkalajatakam atthamam. "}